      "title": "Last year Colorado voted down another unnecessary abortion ban....",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=jx96IN1eFaMAX-Gnctd\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ebc7532302375342179d4b40d10610c9\u0026oe=6025A9FC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3873822052651255/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cp\u003eLast year Colorado voted down another unnecessary abortion ban. This year, we need to say no more bans. Our \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/rjresolution\"\u003e#RJResolution\u003c/a\u003e is to ensure affordable access to the healthcare people need, including abortion, and make sure people can become parents when they are ready. \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/stopthebans\"\u003e#StopTheBans\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3873822052651255/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/135900714_3873822055984588_2484026890621246258_o.png?_nc_cat=109\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=da1649\u0026_nc_ohc=gsjnwHVmBvIAX8yp7MX\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026_nc_tp=30\u0026oh=40b574a88c0892d44facdb7e0d70c184\u0026oe=6023E47A\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says 'WE UP MORE GoptheBars DON'T NEED POLITICIANS PUTTING BARRIERS ABORTION. TO STOP PLAYING BODIES, OUR GAMES POLITICAL FAMILIES AND WITH OUR OUR FUTURES! RResalutans'\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says 'WE UP MORE GoptheBars DON'T NEED POLITICIANS PUTTING BARRIERS ABORTION. TO STOP PLAYING BODIES, OUR GAMES POLITICAL FAMILIES AND WITH OUR OUR FUTURES! RResalutans'\" /\u003e\